The paper also mentions DL-Lite_R, which is a description logic language, and conservative rewriting and approximation, which are techniques used in logic and knowledge representation. Therefore, cs.LO and cs.DL are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of a prototype system, which involves software engineering, making cs.SE a possible sub-category as well.
